org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection

Class RandomUnassignmentSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.RandomUnassignmentSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RndUnProblStudSelection

    public class RandomUnassignmentSelection
extends Object
implements NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>
    Random unassignment of some (randomly selected) students.

    In each step a student is randomly selected with the given probabilty. Null is returned otherwise (controll is passed to the following NeighbourSelection).

    Parameters:
    Related Solver Parameters
    Parameter Type Comment
    Neighbour.RandomUnassignmentProb Double Probability of a random selection of a student.
